{title: Talking With The Wolves}
{artist: Glen Hansard}
{meta: type Chords}

Tune the low E to F
Capo on 2nd fret

[CHORDS]
 * [Am7] * [Dm7] * [Fmaj7] [Am7]    [G]   [Fmaj7] > [Am7] > [Fmaj7] > [G]
